Potion Master- (5)
- Can craft any of these potions to use in the game:
-- Kill potion - Use this to weak attack 2 people at the end of phase.
-- Protection potion - Use this to protect someone from all attacks during the night. If the target is not attacked, the protection will continue on to the next night. (Doesn't expire till attacked) Note that this is a weak protection.
-- Combo Potion - Use this potion to protect 1 person for 1 night (weak protection), and weak attack someone once on the same night at the end of the phase.
- All potions take 2 days to make. The potion master does not lose progress on death. The potion can be used instantly, or later upon completion. Potions can only used for night phases. 
- Respawns in 6 phases.
